  • Classes in MazeObjects used by GameObjects 
    Class and Description
    CustomMazeObject
    the class customMazeObject is used to place custom objects in the maze that are imported from a .obj file Like all MazeObjects, it implements a translate method that returns a copy of the maze object moved to a different location, and a very weak equals method that acts as a somewhat more specific version of the instanceof operator.
